    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1954-06-25T03:02:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1954-06-25T03:02:00-05:00" n="235"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d235">
                <head>235. Telegram From <gloss type="from">Operation <gloss
                            target="#t_PBSPBSUCCESS1">PBSUCCESS</gloss> Headquarters in
                        Florida</gloss> to the <gloss type="to">
                        <gloss target="#t_CIA1">CIA</gloss> Station</gloss> in [<hi rend="italic"
                        >place not declassified</hi>]<note n="1" type="source" xml:id="d235fn1"
                        >Source: Central Intelligence Agency, Job 79–01025A, Box 6, Folder 5.
                        Secret; Priority; RYBAT; <gloss target="#t_PBSPBSUCCESS1">PBSUCCESS</gloss>.
                        Repeated to the Director of Central Intelligence.</note>
                </head>
                <dateline>[<hi rend="italic">place not declassified</hi>], <date
                        calendar="gregorian" when="1954-06-25T08:02:00+00:00">June 25, 1954,
                        0802Z</date>.</dateline>
                <p>4309. Ref: [<hi rend="italic">telegram indicator not declassified</hi>]
                        1102.<note n="2" xml:id="d235fn2">Not found.</note>
                </p>
                <p>1. Through whatever source you consider most appropriate request you get word to
                    erratic if he has any sincere desire to rid <gloss target="#t_WSBURNT1"
                        >WSBURNT</gloss> of communism the best thing he can do is to encourage his
                    people to infiltrate into Esquipulas and report to <persName corresp="#p_CJH1"
                        >Calligeris</persName> for combat duty.</p>
                <p>ERRATIC himself should be encouraged publicly to offer his services to <persName
                        corresp="#p_CJH1">Calligeris</persName> putting aside all past grievances,
                    chips are down. Now is the moment for all anti-Communists to fight shoulder to
                    shoulder. If he willing fine. If only half hearted or still personally ambitious
                    tell him to keep to his hamburger stand.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
